Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:33.30,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}悲寻固己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:49.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}淡觅儚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:07.74,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}顿足仰天  深际蔚蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:18.67,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}揽贫英至
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:25.18,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}爱恋难舍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:30.90,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}唯笑比心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:36.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}只君存依
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:41.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}开往明悉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:54.36,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}遥律破晓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:03:10.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}心渗醉情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:33.30,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみに　試されるたび  少しずつ　強くなってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:49.43,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}ありふれた　毎日の中　夢のつづき　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:07.74,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}歩きつかれて　見上げた空  深く　どこまでも　Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:18.67,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}ちっぽけな自分　抱きしめて  それでも　進んでく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:25.18,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}あなたに会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:30.90,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}笑顔を伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:36.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}あなたがいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:41.01,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}光が生まれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:54.36,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}遥かなる　優しい調べ  遠い宇宙　越えて届くの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:03:10.80,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}胸の奥　かけがえのない  甘い痛み  満ちていく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,======================ED======================
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.61,0:26:14.48,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}黄昏に流れだした
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.66,0:26:18.18,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}制服の群れに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.01,0:26:23.38,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}逆らうよに　自転車の
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.46,0:26:27.63,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}ペダル　思いきり踏んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.92,0:26:32.29,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}放課後のグランドの脇
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.35,0:26:35.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}金網をくぐって
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.83,0:26:41.18,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年　見つけた　ひまわりは
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.29,0:26:45.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年より　誇らしげに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.73,0:26:49.17,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}空を見上げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.96,0:26:54.50,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}折れないように　枯れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.52,0:26:58.29,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}涙に出来たなら
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.91,0:27:05.21,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}明日は何かが変わるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.89,0:27:12.29,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}雨降る日は　雨に揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.30,0:27:16.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}あの　ひまわりみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.90,0:27:20.96,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}まっすぐ　背を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.20,0:27:27.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}今日は揺れていたって、いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.61,0:26:14.48,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}黄昏下  逆行在流动的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.66,0:26:18.18,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}身着制服的人群中
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.01,0:26:23.38,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}尽情地  蹬踩着
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.46,0:26:27.63,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}自行车的脚踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.92,0:26:32.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}放学后  操场边
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.35,0:26:35.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}钻过铁丝网
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.83,0:26:41.18,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年发现的向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.29,0:26:45.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}比以往还要骄傲地
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.73,0:26:49.17,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}仰望着天空
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.96,0:26:54.50,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}不屈不挠  不会枯萎地
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.52,0:26:58.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}若是放声哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.91,0:27:05.21,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}明天又会变得怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.89,0:27:12.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}下雨的日子  在雨中摇摆
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.30,0:27:16.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}就像那朵向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.90,0:27:20.96,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}挺直了腰杆
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.20,0:27:27.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}哪怕今日有所动摇  也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  夕子她？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她非常讨厌爸爸你的这个习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是问了朋友也只有你一个人这么不干净
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子是那么说的？对你？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  哥哥  那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些烟是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  也让我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  我说哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下可惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是园原基地的方向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:05.73,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(268,360)\fs13\fr-8}园原基地周围地区发生山林火灾？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}刚才的烟和火灾的红光…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.41,0:01:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}在园原基地发生的爆炸是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水前寺邦博
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:22.94,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(480,360)\fs29}水前寺 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事情相信大家都听说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  今天课就上到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人马上放学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我安静！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了你们的安全着想才采取的措施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了这是紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到下个返校日前就老老实实待在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  浅羽  还有西久保
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家路上绕到哪里去逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是河口让我们尽早回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动铅笔  一直在用的不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你好像也说\N橡皮还是尺什么的不见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶穗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是马上就会开战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽  快来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正要去取材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  负责在我们的期刊上\N写文章介绍美食商铺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么类型都有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正要出去取材\N就想伊里野要不要也一块去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  河口的话不用理会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是难得的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野还一次都没有\N进行过取材和撰写报导吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟伊里野也是新闻部的部员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连浅羽的程度都做不到的话会很头痛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去还是不去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不战而胜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要去的是蛋糕店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐巴士10分钟左右的路程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙黄白毫和草莓芭菲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和晶穗一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是在偷听…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者应该说是偷看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很甜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油泡芙和冰酿咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和晶穗一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美乃滋酱油意大利面和奶油苏打
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和晶穗一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用小盘子盛来吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…取材吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点反胃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊  女生的甜食胃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把我跟晶穗归为一类啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野没来参加学园祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野也来参加学园祭该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因为新闻部的企划要出号外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和浅羽到处去取材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂「号外」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就是和浅羽一起吃炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和浅羽一起吃烤白薯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和浅羽一起在篝火晚会上跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后那一项…是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  去采访下一家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多都吃得下的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:07:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁人套餐一份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和晶穗一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊…客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是先说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店的铁餐是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁人套餐一份！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和晶穗一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:17.67,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fs17}免费饮食列传\N铁人套餐\N价格四千日元\N（铁人拉面+铁人饺子+铁人中华大盖饭）\N全部吃完则不收取费用\N限制时间六十分钟\N中途离席、以及把四周弄得脏兮兮的情况下将直接结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}铁餐两份！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,60分钟内无法吃完时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把桌子弄得脏兮兮时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就直接结束并收取4000日元的费用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  至少要吃掉一半哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  将手离开桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部吃完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶穗呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊  看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着是铁人饺子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将手离开桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫！ 烫烫烫…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退后！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  真是场精彩的比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  看好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一定是这边的短发孩子赢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你没看到她刚才都快要吐出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中华大盖饭来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更换裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是本店的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓如月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论结果如何这都是最后一盘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望两位都不要留下任何遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么将手离开桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  不要插手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是老大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该医生叫停了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会输给晶穗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对…不会输！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶穗  加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野别输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃啊！  吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野  醒着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很怕…你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我一起去取材的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕得腿发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得一定会被带到没人的地方\N然后痛打一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我逃走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很怕你  但我怎么能认输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一直都这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从最初见到你开始直到刚才  我都很怕你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胃药买来了  胃药
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破最低年龄记录了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈噗 「噗」的流出鼻血来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  那个「加奈噗」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我胃药
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野也要吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊？  这个大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么下午没有打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩得忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我硬邀她一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来！  你到底是谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 那是加奈噗的哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体情况我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我介绍说是姓榎本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  浅羽之前遇到过这个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  实际聊过后觉得是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是很关心伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.82,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈噗  你染发了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:03.10,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是淡银灰色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:03.10,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(334,441)\fs20}platinum blonde
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:04.92,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形象改变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.20,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:09.57,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:10.47,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回座…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.82,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:16.56,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  不是的  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:17.51,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:18.54,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪开！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:19.62,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:20.52,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.66,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候染这么个头发算什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:24.64,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.45,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个并不是特意染的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:31.06,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  虽然我们也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:31.89,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:37.74,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  伊里野一直都在吃很多药
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.66,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是药的副作用…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.41,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就染回来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.35,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  站起来  到办公室去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:48.73,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}伊里野加奈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:51.15,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}田中先生来电
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.49,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}请你速到办公室来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:54.03,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}伊里野加奈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:55.46,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}请你速到办公室来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:00.53,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:09.90,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:16.68,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.33,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才是第一节课
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:21.22,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样来学校不就没意义了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:23.56,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:33.25,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子他妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:35.38,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把报纸抽走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.63,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:37.98,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:40.56,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连天气预报都没有  真头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:43.91,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}致各位观众\N\N现在，将依\N照国土防卫\N新法对情报\N进行管制。\N根据有事对\N策准则非法\N使用电波将\N构成重大违\N法行为。\N自卫军治安\N部队也正在\N加强对非官\N方广播的取\N缔工作。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:43.30,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是情报管制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.28,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拐角的坂井先生好像也要被疏散了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:48.68,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才来告过别了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:51.77,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变冷清了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:59.22,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs29}安静！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:58.92,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 晶穗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:01.57,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  所以和花村一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:03.63,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听从父母请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:06.22,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她还说托你照顾伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.04,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  简直像是幼儿园的保育员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.96,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野  原来你在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:36.99,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.35,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我  知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:42.83,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见  我看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:43.97,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:45.14,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.04,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看见的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:46.94,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.58,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:50.73,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.72,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能说的话  那就不要说罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:02.43,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说也行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:05.30,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:23.01,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压住她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:43.45,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时看得见  有时看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:45.58,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种突发性的视觉异常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.74,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是从现在才开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:50.90,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这么严重倒还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:55.24,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这样了为什么还要来学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:01.20,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:03.59,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.65,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是「浅羽袋」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:16.40,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  她是把这些东西当作护身符吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:24.29,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管去哪里不管做什么都会随身携带
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.26,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢  虽然确实是加奈不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.51,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过希望你不要生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:33.81,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于加奈来说\N护身符真的是攸关生死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:34.49,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:40.76,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野是那个Black Manta的驾驶员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.81,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手腕嵌着金属球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:48.94,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会突然留鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:51.17,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至头发一下子变白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.77,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在眼睛也看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:55.78,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是因为伊里野是\NBlack Manta的驾驶员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.23,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无人知晓的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:01.33,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野在和敌人战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:06.97,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事大人来做  不就好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:09.79,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们擅自引发的战争吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:13.81,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那种事一定要让伊里野来做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:17.00,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有伊里野要这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:18.96,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口插满针筒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:21.34,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满身是血地倒在这里不可啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:25.03,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:34.18,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽同学  我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:46.68,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宰了你  这个臭小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:51.07,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:53.27,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却在这里信口开河
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:57.57,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装得一副只有自己才理解加奈的嘴脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:02.46,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  你到底都知道加奈的什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:07.38,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无知者的善意根本就是不负责任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:10.90,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就只有喂野猫的觉悟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:30.37,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把加奈送回保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:36.68,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会…接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:23.78,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个钟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:27.22,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,键盘上的鼠标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.19,0:22:29.59,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书架上的布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.44,0:22:33.77,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是部长的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:36.20,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:38.61,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:40.12,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:41.87,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为灯亮着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:46.29,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:48.21,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:51.64,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…为了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.26,0:23:01.92,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今…都没有…一次都…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:08.85,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护身符什么的…没有…想…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.51,0:23:11.11,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.57,0:23:18.23,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要过…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.35,0:23:23.20,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:26.39,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长马上就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:29.14,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长的话  一定能做些什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.82,0:23:31.41,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长什么都会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.00,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野的事情也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:45.68,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:46.93,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:49.26,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长？ 是部长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.63,0:23:50.52,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在人在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:51.25,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话亭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:52.76,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.47,0:23:55.10,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边情况很严重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.33,0:23:57.28,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  这里也很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.55,0:23:58.71,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.99,0:24:00.04,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是生物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.77,0:24:01.91,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:02.86,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.11,0:24:05.22,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽特派员 那是生物！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.17,0:24:08.82,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.93,0:24:10.91,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园原电波新闻部不会向镇压屈服！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:13.02,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有报导自由…！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.12,0:24:14.61,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了！  你们这群混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.59,0:24:26.20,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.14,0:24:30.72,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我不会问第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.62,0:24:35.41,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要现在马上回去基地？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.60,0:24:38.67,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是希望让我来帮你？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.49,0:24:54.08,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.74,0:24:55.50,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.60,0:24:58.28,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起伊里野不用再回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.36,0:25:01.98,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到伊里野自己想回去的时候再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.01,0:25:05.74,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  马上就会被抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.46,0:25:08.98,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我会和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.17,0:25:09.67,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.14,0:25:10.76,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.21,0:25:13.54,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为浅羽身上有虫
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.31,0:25:20.73,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电池虫和电波虫
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.04,0:25:23.70,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,载有发信芯片的生化植入系统
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.04,0:25:23.70,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(254,441)\fs20}transponder chip
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.04,0:25:23.70,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(414,441)\fs20}bioimplant
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.74,0:25:30.55,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…会被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.46,0:25:36.04,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.90,0:25:37.90,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.67,0:25:51.98,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅羽  痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.87,0:25:53.93,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.26,0:25:56.39,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事


